description.zh:

第一次自提出隐藏！店员的手气太好了！感激！
description.en:
"Preface": When I saw it was online again, I thought it would be online the same as before and I would resume offline the next day. I still underestimated the labubu. Last night I found that I could no longer buy the wholesale, so I could only place a single box and decisively placed a four-order single box. I went to pick up the goods today, and I felt something was wrong when I shook one of them. There was no space up or down, and there was a vague plastic shell. Isn’t this hiding the feel!
『Weight』: 126.3g, calculated as the weight of the middle echelon
"Touch": There is no space up and down, and there is also a top (can be pressed to the plastic shell), and you can feel the plastic shell slightly when you shake it. The left and right are not moved as a whole, and the front and back are slightly moved, and only touch the box on the back (such as p2)
"Place": See p2, it is placed obliquely in the box, the whole is a columnar, without any accessories.
The first time I asked to hide it! The clerk’s luck is so good! gratitude!
